61
00:03:33,370 --> 00:03:36,920
where researchers were looking at a
particular genetic variant.

62
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:40,350
And they were able to show that this
genetic variant was statistically

63
00:03:40,350 --> 00:03:43,100
associated with moderate to severe
cellulite.

64
00:03:43,100 --> 00:03:44,690
So it was a case controlled study.

65
00:03:44,690 --> 00:03:45,820
Here's the data from that study.

66
00:03:45,820 --> 00:03:47,030
They sampled 200 cases.

67
00:03:47,030 --> 00:03:50,030
These are women who have, moderate to
severe cellulite.

68
00:03:50,030 --> 00:03:53,660
And 200 controls, women who did not have
moderate to severe cellulite.

69
00:03:53,660 --> 00:03:57,020
And then they tested them for this
particular genotype.

70
00:03:57,020 --> 00:04:02,480
And if you carried a D allele, there, that
