71
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:05,570
risk of having moderate to severe
cellulite in this case control study.

72
00:04:05,570 --> 00:04:06,640
Here are the numbers.

73
00:04:06,640 --> 00:04:10,375
So, when you get a positive on the
CelluliteDX test,

74
00:04:10,375 --> 00:04:13,437
all that means is that you carry a D
allele.

75
00:04:13,437 --> 00:04:18,194
So let's, that, so again, the same numbers
are used for, if you have a positive on

76
00:04:18,194 --> 00:04:22,580
the CelluliteDX test, that's the same as,
as having this genetic allele.

77
00:04:22,580 --> 00:04:25,334
So now let's look at the test and who, and
the, and the, and

78
00:04:25,334 --> 00:04:28,412
who actually has the disease, and right
from this two by two table,

79
00:04:28,412 --> 00:04:31,350
we can calculate from these data
