83
00:04:41,777 --> 00:04:43,214
let's do it from a two by two table now.

84
00:04:43,214 --> 00:04:44,781
So what's the sensitivity here?

85
00:04:44,781 --> 00:04:49,214
So there are 200 women who truly have
cellulite.

86
00:04:49,214 --> 00:04:51,983
Out of those women, those are the case
women,

87
00:04:51,983 --> 00:04:54,687
168 of them tested positive on this test.

88
00:04:54,687 --> 00:04:57,683
So that would make the sensitivity 84%.

89
00:04:57,683 --> 00:05:01,672
Notice that there were 32 women who
