183
00:10:04,770 --> 00:10:07,480
So, the first thing is, your either one of
these women get destined to

184
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:08,970
get the cellulite or you're not.

185
00:10:08,970 --> 00:10:13,101
That's 65% prevalence and 1 minus 65% is
35%, so

186
00:10:13,101 --> 00:10:15,730
that's whether or not you truly have the
disease.

187
00:10:17,090 --> 00:10:20,740
Then, you are either going to test
positive on this CelluliteDX test or not.

188
00:10:20,740 --> 00:10:23,980
If you actually have the disease, the
sensitivity again is 84%,

189
00:10:23,980 --> 00:10:26,823
so your chance of not testing positive is
16%.

190
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:32,750
If you don't have the disease, you still
have a 74% chance of testing positive, and

191
00:10:32,750 --> 00:10:35,350
you have a 26% chance of not testing
positive.

192
00:10:35,350 --> 00:10:37,790
We can multiply across the branches, so

193
00:10:37,790 --> 00:10:42,916
the upper branch is .546, this one is
.104.

194
00:10:42,916 --> 00:10:47,570
This one is .259, this one is .091.

195
00:10:47,570 --> 00:10:49,560
I just got those by multiplying across the
branches.

196
00:10:49,560 --> 00:10:54,310
Notice if I add all these up, it sums up
to exactly 1, so I've done it right.

197
00:10:54,310 --> 00:10:57,780
So now, once I know that you've tested
positive, I,

198
00:10:57,780 --> 00:11:01,380
then I know that you're either on this
branch, or your on this branch.

