211
00:11:38,780 --> 00:11:42,900
So, to solve for positive predictive and
negative predictive value,

212
00:11:42,900 --> 00:11:47,510
you could incorporate the true prevalence
by just doing a little 2 by 2 table and

213
00:11:47,510 --> 00:11:50,250
assuming that you have a denominator of
